	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001137_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>50 Albemarle St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p>21<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">st</hi></hi> Nov<hi rend="sup">r</hi></p>
<lb/><p>1857 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Sir </p>
<lb/><p>On my return 
<lb/>From <placeName>Oxford</placeName> I 
<lb/>found your 
<lb/>favour of the 
<lb/>18<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> enclosing 
<lb/>a Dft for Â£31.4 
<lb/>being an addition 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001137_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>to the Testimonial fund 
<lb/>from <placeName>Dundee</placeName> and 
<lb/>I now beg to 
<lb/>return you my 
<lb/>hearty thanks 
<lb/>for your very great kindness 
<lb/>in reference to 
<lb/>this and the 
<lb/>rest of that fund<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I shall ever look  
<lb/>back to the 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001137_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>unexpected generosity 
<lb/>of the people at 
<lb/><placeName>Dundee</placeName> with feelings 
<lb/>of gratitude and 
<lb/>regret that 
<lb/>previous exertions 
<lb/>in <placeName>Edinburgh</placeName>
<lb/>had so "knocked 
<lb/>me up" that I 
<lb/>could not well 
<lb/>express what 
<lb/>I meant when 
<lb/>with you<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001137_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/>I believe the whole 
<lb/>sum you mention 
<lb/>was united to the 
<lb/><placeName>London</placeName> Fund, but 
<lb/>it would as you 
<lb/>think have been 
<lb/>better had it come 
<lb/>direct as I am proud 
<lb/>of my connection 
<lb/>with <placeName>Scotland</placeName>. I 
<lb/>thank you also 
<lb/>for kindly forwarding 
<lb/>the copies sent 
<lb/>of the book and am 
<lb/>gratefully yours </p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
